  <?dbhtml filename="videoproto.html"?>

  <title>videoproto-&videoproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension provides a protocol for a video output mechanism, mainly to
      rescale video playback in the video controller hardware.
    </para>

